Class WMSNamespaceContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.worldwind.util.BasicNamespaceContext
      • gov.nasa.worldwind.wms.WMSNamespaceContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NamespaceContext

    public class WMSNamespaceContext
extends BasicNamespaceContext
    WMSNamespaceContext is an implementation of NamespaceContext which provides an XML Namespace context necessary for parsing WMS documents, such as a WMS Capabilities document.
